000, "description": "http://www.zwsub.com/course/Design-Thinking-Understanding-the-Process.html\\n完整课程参看 http://www.zwsub.com/course/Design-Thinking-Understanding-the-Process.html\\n课程476938英文名称:Design Thinking: Understanding", "source": "bilibili", "query": "Thinking Process:", "page": 1}, {"title": "Critical Thinking- Why, How Examples", "bvid": "BV13K4y1t7DC", "url": "http://www.bilibili.com/video/av883204883", "author": "无关烟雨", "duration": "5:44", "duration_seconds": 344.0, "play": 1653, "description": "https://r5---sn-npoeene7.googlevideo.com/videoplayback?expire=1589488146&amp;ei=slW9XtmHHoXSwgT3spzAAg&amp;ip=177.22.107.142&amp;id=o-AB96BOqnNFlRU_cMg_LThe8seqvrNNzPTm5vL5kZiCPb&amp;itag=22&amp;sourc", "source": "bilibili", "query": "Thinking Process:", "page": 1}, {"title": "claude code：深入讲解thinking模式", "bvid": "BV14dyVBtEam", "url": "http://www.bilibili.com/video/av115571513364495", "author": "ClaudeEvangelist", "duration": "5:38", "duration_seconds": 338.0, "play": 371, "description": "Claude Code 中“思考模式”是一种增强型计算状态，专为解决复杂问题而设计。思考模式会分配额外的处理时间，使 Claude 能够在生成输出之前评估各种方案并进行更深入的分析。用户可以通过按下 Tab 键或使用特定的触发词*来激活此模式，例如“认真思考”或“超强思考”，这些触发词对应于不同的资源分配级别。强烈建议在要求 AI 编写任何代码之前，使用思考模式进行规划和架构决策，这样可以防止 A", "source": "bilibili", "query": "Thinking Process:", "page": 1}, {"title": "How to get unstuck using design thinking process 如何利用设计思维来摆脱生活困境", "bvid": "BV1tb4y197Wj", "url": "http://www.bilibili.com/video/av629622153", "author": "负根号3", "duration": "9:38", "duration_seconds": 578.0, "play": 41, "description": "我2021年初在youtube开通了自己的频道，主要是分享自己在工作和生活着的感悟，希望和大家分享一起进步。\\n\\n通过国内朋友推荐，开通了B站，这是我在B站上传的第一个视频，希望大家提供宝贵意见。", "source": "bilibili", "query": "Thinking Process:", "page": 1}, {"title": "【八分钟播客】 为什么用英语思考很难？｜How To Start Thinking In English", "bvid": "BV1VVyeYMEWU", "url": "http://www.bilibili.com/video/av113340210745202", "author": "学习星球", "duration": "9:36", "duration_seconds": 576.0, "play": 67723, "description": "YouTube\\n今天你会学到什么：\\n\\n理解挑战：为什么用英语思考很难？我们将用简单的术语来解释它。\\n帮助你的简单技巧